Day 11: Own the Retrospective!
🔄 "The Retrospective is the team's mirror—what does your reflection show?"  
👉 Tip: Use retrospectives to uncover blind spots and continuously improve. It’s not just about looking back but stepping forward.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
